Class StochasticSamplingSubnetLayer

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MultiPrecision<StochasticSamplingSubnetLayer>, Layer, ReferenceCounting, StochasticComponent, Serializable

    public class StochasticSamplingSubnetLayer
extends WrapperLayer
implements StochasticComponent, MultiPrecision<StochasticSamplingSubnetLayer>
    This layer works as a scaling function, similar to a father wavelet. Allows convolutional and pooling layers to work across larger image regions.
